<H1>Seven years in Tibet</H1>
<Font Color=#4c4c4c>
FILM NAME :Seven years in Tibet<BR>
Release date : 15/6<BR>
Staring :Brad Pit & David Thewellis<BR>
<Font Color=#00ccff>
<P>
Based on a true story following 2 German climbers at World War 2. The climbers <BR>
are captured by British forces, But manage to escape and eventually stumble across<BR>
The Dali Lama's home city. Pitt's meeting  with the head Dali Lama changes his   <BR>
attitude on life. Content with his new life He is then forced to flee.<BR>
This is due to the ever mounting threat from china.<BR>
<P>
<P>
<Font Color=#FFFFFF>
IN SHORT:- A good film with  good performances from Pitt & Thewellis.<BR>
This film benefits from the fact that it stems from a true story,<BR>
And not a Hollywood plotless wonder!<BR>
<P>
<Font Color=#FF0000>
VERDICT :- 7/10
